OL,3,CMan detained under Mental Health Act
OL,4,Cafter James Bulger's grave damaged
OL,6,FA man has been detained under the
OL,7,FMental Health Act after the grave of
OL,8,Fmurdered toddler James Bulger was
OL,9,Fvandalised.
OL,11,FOfficers from Merseyside Police were
OL,12,Fcalled to Kirkdale Cemetery in
OL,13,FLiverpool on Friday, 10 April at
OL,14,Faround 1.20pm.
OL,16,FA 78-year-old man from Lancashire was
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of criminal
OL,18,Fdamage and theft.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
