OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781849901
OL,3,CMan detained under Mental Health Act
OL,4,Cafter James Bulger's grave damaged
OL,6,FHe was taken to a police station in
OL,7,FMerseyside and later detained under
OL,8,FSection 3 of the Mental Health Act.
OL,10,FHe is now in a mental health hospital
OL,11,Fand will remain there for care and
OL,12,Ftreatment.
OL,14,FJames was two-years-old when he was
OL,15,Fabducted from shopping centre in
OL,16,FBootle and murdered by 10-year-old
OL,17,Fboys Robert Thompson and Jon Venables
OL,18,Fin 1993.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
