PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781849901
OL,3,CMan detained under Mental Health Act
OL,4,Cafter James Bulger's grave damaged
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jemma Berry said:
OL,7,F"The 78-year-old man was detained
OL,8,Funder section 3 of the Mental Health
OL,9,FAct 1983 under compulsory detention.
OL,11,F"During the investigation detectives
OL,12,Festablished that several graves were
OL,13,Ftargeted within Kirkdale Cemetery.
OL,15,F"Stolen ornaments from gravestones
OL,16,Fwere also recovered by our officers
OL,17,Fduring the investigation and have now
OL,18,Fbeen returned to the rightful families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
