PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781849901
OL,3,CMan detained under Mental Health Act
OL,4,Cafter James Bulger's grave damaged
OL,6,F"I would also like to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to thank James' family and
OL,8,Fthe other families whose gravestones
OL,9,Fwere damaged for their ongoing support
OL,10,Fthroughout our investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
